divs: Sighting DetailsI went to the park near our home with my wife and dogs on May 6th, 2007 I think it was around 12-2pm. I was taking alot of photographs with my new camera Sony 7.2 megapixel. I set the camera at the highest setting and took two photos one of a kite flying, and one of the mountains with the clouds above them. Upon returning home I uploaded the photos into my computer as I was going through the pics I saw something strange on the left corner of the picture above the street light their was a cylindrical object laying horizontal to the ground, but about a 1000 feet over the mountains which I believe are about 1500 to 2000 feet up. As I zoomed in the hair stood up on my arms! I was a cylinder! Then I quickly looked through the other pictures when on my 3 pic I saw another strange thing in the picture. This was the picture of the kite flying, this time I see what looks like a gray disc. When I enlarged it to 200% then 400% I freaked, it was a classic saucer shaped craft! Look for yourselves and please tell me what you see. Thanks, Frank Im concerned about the quality of the pics that I send you. On my photo program (picasa) it enlarges really clear and not pixelated at all. I hope you have the same. If not let me know then maybe I can upload it right from my pic card. thanks, F
Summary: UFO's showed up on digital pictures I was taking at the park
